mittee  and  the  authors  of  this  bill  to—and  NHTSA—to  make  sure 
that we achieve an objective that I think we share. 

Mr.  Chairman,  I  could  go  into  detail,  but,  perhaps  in  questions, 
with  regard  to  S.  1948  that  was  introduced  yesterday,  I  think  the 

